msgid "Limit Police"
msgstr "限速管控"

msgid "Edit rule"
msgstr "编辑规则"

msgid "Traffic Report"
msgstr "流量统计"

msgid ""
"Per-device bandwidth policing using <code>tc ingress police</code>. Stays "
"compatible with hardware Flow Offloading, fullcon NAT, and BBR. No IFB, no "
"HTB, no fq_codel, no Cake."
msgstr ""
"用 <code>tc ingress police</code>（TC 入向流量管制）对每台设备做带宽限速。"
"兼容硬件 Flow Offloading、fullcon NAT、BBR；不依赖 IFB / HTB / fq_codel / "
"Cake。"

msgid "Service"
msgstr "服务"

msgid "Enable service"
msgstr "启用服务"

msgid ""
"When enabled, rules below are pushed via <code>/etc/init.d/limitpolice</code>."
msgstr ""
"启用后，下方规则会通过 <code>/etc/init.d/limitpolice</code> 下发到内核。"

msgid "Stats / quota poll interval (seconds)"
msgstr "流量统计 / 配额轮询间隔（秒）"

msgid ""
"How often the daemon runs <code>limitpolice-quota-check</code>. Minimum 10s. "
"5 minutes (300) is the safe default on weak CPUs."
msgstr ""
"守护进程跑 <code>limitpolice-quota-check</code> 的频率。最短 10 秒。"
"弱 CPU 推荐 5 分钟（300）。"

msgid "Stats archive interval (seconds)"
msgstr "流量统计归档间隔（秒）"

msgid ""
"How often the daemon runs <code>limitpolice-stats-backup</code> (single "
"tar.gz write to <code>/etc/limitpolice/</code>). Minimum 60s. 1 hour (3600) "
"is the safe default — protects against active reboot only; power loss can "
"lose up to one interval."
msgstr ""
"守护进程跑 <code>limitpolice-stats-backup</code> 的频率（往 <code>/etc/"
"limitpolice/</code> 写一次 tar.gz）。最短 60 秒。1 小时（3600）只防主动"
"重启，掉电会丢一个间隔的数据。"

msgid "Quota throttle rate (kbit)"
msgstr "配额惩罚速率（kbit）"

msgid ""
"Rate the offending filter is dropped to when a device's daily quota is "
"exceeded. <code>1</code> = hard wall (default). Raise to <code>16</code> or "
"<code>64</code> to keep basic IM text flowing."
msgstr ""
"设备超额后，规则会被降到该速率。<code>1</code> = 完全断网（默认）。调到 "
"<code>16</code> 或 <code>64</code> 可保留 IM 文字收发。"

msgid "Service control"
msgstr "服务控制"

msgid "Current status"
msgstr "当前状态"

msgid "Per-device rules"
msgstr "按设备的规则"

msgid "Enable"
msgstr "启用"

msgid "Interface"
msgstr "网络接口"

msgid "Match by"
msgstr "匹配方式"

msgid "Target"
msgstr "目标"

msgid "Either type a value above, or click a chip below."
msgstr "在上方输入值，或点下方 DHCP 列表中的设备。"

msgid "Direction"
msgstr "方向"

msgid "Downlink (to this device)"
msgstr "下行（到本设备）"

msgid "Uplink (from this device)"
msgstr "上行（来自本设备）"

msgid ""
"<b>dst</b> caps packets <em>to</em> the device → pair with a WAN-side iface "
"(where packets from the internet first arrive, e.g. <code>wan</code>, "
"<code>pppoe-wan</code>, <code>eth1</code>).<br/><b>src</b> caps packets "
"<em>from</em> the device → pair with a LAN-side iface (where packets from "
"the device first arrive, e.g. <code>br-lan</code>, <code>eth0</code>).<br/"
">Wrong pairing = rule matches zero packets = silently wasted slot."
msgstr ""
"<b>dst</b>（下行）限制到本设备的流量 → 必须配 WAN 侧接口（即互联网流量"
"最先到达的接口，例如 <code>wan</code>、<code>pppoe-wan</code>、"
"<code>eth1</code>）。<br/><b>src</b>（上行）限制本设备发出的流量 → 必须"
"配 LAN 侧接口（即设备流量最先到达的接口，例如 <code>br-lan</code>、"
"<code>eth0</code>）。<br/>方向和接口配错 = 规则匹配零个包 = 静默"
"浪费一条规则。"

msgid "Rate"
msgstr "速率"

msgid "Unit"
msgstr "单位"

msgid "Kbps (kilobits per second)"
msgstr "Kbps（千比特/秒）"

msgid "Mbps (megabits per second)"
msgstr "Mbps（兆比特/秒）"

msgid "KB/s (kilobytes per second)"
msgstr "KB/s（千字节/秒）"

msgid "MB/s (megabytes per second)"
msgstr "MB/s（兆字节/秒）"

msgid "Daily quota (0 = off)"
msgstr "每日配额（0 = 关闭）"

msgid ""
"When exceeded, this device's filter is dropped to <code>1 kbit</code> as a "
"punitive block until the next 00:00 reset. Counters are derived from "
"<code>tc -s filter show</code> bytes, so the value reflects the actual "
"ingress bytes seen on this iface, not the post-NAT traffic. No daemon — a "
"cron job runs the check every 5 min."
msgstr ""
"设备用满配额后，规则会被压到 <code>1 kbit</code> 作为惩罚，次日 00:00 自动"
"恢复。计数器来自 <code>tc -s filter show</code> 的字节数，反映接口上"
"实际见到的入向字节（NAT 之前），不是 NAT 之后的流量。守护进程每 "
"<code>stats_interval</code> 秒检查一次（默认 300 秒，即 5 分钟）。"

msgid "Quota unit"
msgstr "配额单位"

msgid "Note"
msgstr "备注"

msgid "Pick from DHCP"
msgstr "从 DHCP 选"

msgid "No DHCP leases found at /tmp/dhcp.leases."
msgstr "在 /tmp/dhcp.leases 找不到 DHCP 租约。"

msgid ""
"Edit a single per-device bandwidth rule. Save & Apply will restart the init "
"script."
msgstr "编辑单条按设备的限速规则。保存并应用会重启 init 脚本。"

msgid "Rule"
msgstr "规则"

msgid "Either an IPv4/CIDR or a colon-separated MAC."
msgstr "输入 IPv4 / CIDR（如 192.168.1.100/32）或冒号分隔的 MAC 地址。"

msgid ""
"<b>dst</b> caps packets <em>to</em> the device → pair with a WAN-side iface "
"(e.g. <code>wan</code>, <code>pppoe-wan</code>, <code>eth1</code>).<br/"
"><b>src</b> caps packets <em>from</em> the device → pair with a LAN-side "
"iface (e.g. <code>br-lan</code>, <code>eth0</code>).<br/>Wrong pairing = "
"rule matches zero packets = silently wasted slot."
msgstr ""
"<b>dst</b>（下行）限制到本设备的流量 → 必须配 WAN 侧接口（如 "
"<code>wan</code>、<code>pppoe-wan</code>、<code>eth1</code>）。<br/"
"><b>src</b>（上行）限制本设备发出的流量 → 必须配 LAN 侧接口（如 "
"<code>br-lan</code>、<code>eth0</code>）。<br/>方向和接口配错 = 规则"
"匹配零个包 = 静默浪费一条规则。"

msgid ""
"When exceeded, this device's filter is dropped to the throttle rate "
"configured in the main section until the next 00:00 reset. Counted from "
"<code>tc -s filter show</code> bytes."
msgstr ""
"设备用满配额后，规则会被压到主配置中的"惩罚速率"，次日 00:00 自动恢复。"
"计数器来自 <code>tc -s filter show</code> 的字节数。"

msgid "Per-device daily / weekly / monthly traffic derived from"
msgstr "每台设备的日 / 周 / 月流量，来自"

msgid ""
"counters maintained by a cron job. Counts reset on reboot (no flash "
"writes). Open the main"
msgstr ""
"计数器由守护进程维护。计数器随重启清零（不写 flash，保护 UBIFS）。"
"打开主"

msgid "page to add rate-limit or daily-quota rules."
msgstr "页面可加限速或配额规则。"

msgid ""
"No stats yet. The cron job runs every 5 minutes — check back after a few "
"cycles. You can verify with:"
msgstr ""
"暂无统计数据。守护进程每 <code>stats_interval</code> 秒跑一次（默认 300 秒）"
"，稍等几个周期后再来刷新。可用以下命令验证："

msgid "Device"
msgstr "设备"

msgid "MAC / IP"
msgstr "MAC / IP"

msgid "Today ↓"
msgstr "今日 ↓"

msgid "Today ↑"
msgstr "今日 ↑"

msgid "Week ↓"
msgstr "本周 ↓"

msgid "Week ↑"
msgstr "本周 ↑"

msgid "Month ↓"
msgstr "本月 ↓"

msgid "Month ↑"
msgstr "本月 ↑"

msgid "Last seen"
msgstr "最后活跃"

msgid "Quick config"
msgstr "快捷配置"

msgid "Add a real-time rate limit for this device"
msgstr "给该设备加一条实时限速规则"

msgid "Limit"
msgstr "限速"

msgid "Add a daily quota for this device"
msgstr "给该设备加一条每日配额"

msgid "Quota"
msgstr "配额"

msgid ""
"Unknown devices (greyed) have no DHCP lease — usually static-IP hosts or "
"devices that have not yet completed DHCP. Use the IP-based quick-config "
"button to add a rule manually."
msgstr ""
"未知设备（灰色行）没有 DHCP 租约 — 通常是静态 IP 主机，或尚未完成 DHCP "
"的设备。用基于 IP 的"快捷配置"按钮手动加规则。"